snippet.title: Last Oasis - Steam Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Man your walkers and keep moving, the world is dying!

Wishlist on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/903950/Last_Oasis/

Last Oasis is a Nomadic Survival MMO. Earth has stopped rotating, and the last human survivors need to outrun the scorching sun in a massive Open World. Join the nomads on their wind-powered walking machines with designs inspired by Theo Jansen's amazing strandbeests. 

STEAM - https://store.steampowered.com/app/903950/Last_Oasis/
DISCORD - https://discord.gg/lastoasis
TWITTER - https://twitter.com/OasisNomad
WEBSITE - https://lastoasis.gg
